{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-greetings-in-your-first-day-at-the-office/task-143","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-greetings-in-your-first-day-at-the-office","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da bi se pokazalo vlasništvo, obično dodaje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">'s</span> po imenu, kao što je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sophie's desk</span>.</p>\n<p>Međutim, za imena koja se završavaju sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">s</span>, često dodaje znak apostrofa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">'</span>. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">James' book</span>. To znači da je knjiga od Jamesa.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-greetings-in-your-first-day-at-the-office/task-143"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Izaberite ispravno vlasništvo za imena <span class=\"highlighted-text\">server</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">devices</span>.</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Server maintenances, devices manual</span></p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Server maintenances</span> na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">devices manual</span> ne pokazuje pripadnost. Zapamtite da je potreban <span class=\"highlighted-text\">'s</span> ili apostrof za pokazivanje da nešto pripada osobi ili stvari.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Server's maintenance, devices' manual</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Server's maintenance, device's manual</span></p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Server's</span> je tačno za posedovanje jedne osobe, ali budite pažljivi na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">device's</span>. Razmis